                <h2>The Flowers K.G. and High School</h2>
                <p>The Flowers K.G. and High School is a famous school all over the Sylhet division. It is situated in
                    the Court Road of Moulvibazar. It has five academic buildings. Kindergarten and high school seats
                    are available here. A total of 1800 students study here. For the students, 60 teachers are engaged
                    all the time. The students are very fresh-minded and meritorius. The teachers provide proper
                    guidelines to the students. The students are expert in extra-curricular activities apart from
                    textbooks.</p>
